overview: Paul Canon and contractor Mike Stone make their way towards the bathroom to discuss potential alterations, but Paul would rather do a different kind of pipe cleaning. Ty Thomas doesn't usually cruise the parks for hookups, but when he sees Steve Rogers he decides to have a seat. Alex Chandler knocks on Roman Todd's door to confront him but his thoughts quickly turn from anger to enchantment. Connor Halsted eagerly invites Logan Cross back to his place and once there, he tells Logan he's gonna rock his world!
title: Raw Encounters
